{"tid":1267280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"續強烈建議連尼住先生暫停新會員申請","createTime":"2019-06-29T19:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T06:22:59.000Z","uid":85051,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58f9a1047c815f131b1c595dc317b92eb21e4b11","tid":1267280,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:41:02.000Z","msg":"因為巴打個正post爆咗<br />\n我幫手開定一個<br />\n<br />\n暫停理由如下:<br />\n<br />\n1 防止有更多鬼係度搞分化<br />\n<br />\n2 連登係香港人唯一一個網絡大台，太重要，唔可以有任何差池<br />\n<br />\n3 連尼住先生你為我地已經頂咗好多壓力，在此不勝感激。為免有更多敵方勢力俾更多壓力，暫停新申請係有效的。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我都唔想有日失去連登</span><br />\n<br />\n請三思"},{"pid":"062cd2d7cd84bc1197974307ade1f76284e4f191","tid":1267280,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:41:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8a0cd071fa7c5151ca8149e73c46a6d7592ffa8","tid":1267280,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:41:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7202f242ca60163e22c66171400152921397d5ca","tid":1267280,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:41:47.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"e16f8f2c0425e3731e23894d3b5eecbcd02bf5bd","tid":1267280,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:41:57.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"56f1588a141631bf1ae77c90cc6c90ec2e1a37b0","tid":1267280,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:42:32.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"44225b34c2c17f634cf17af7ebe7fed4460167c5","tid":1267280,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:42:56.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"96a2d062d0bb692bd0fc0eec420e7a1d5b36d97a","tid":1267280,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:43:11.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"eaeeb3bcb0801298faab42f71e9e2ad057c32853","tid":1267280,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:43:22.000Z","msg"